msgid ""
"Native bindings via `perry-ext-moment` (v0.5.549). `moment` is in "
"maintenance mode upstream — prefer `dayjs` for new code, but Perry supports "
"both for existing codebases."
msgstr "`perry-ext-moment` 経由のネイティブバインディング（v0.5.549）。`moment` は上流ではメンテナンスモードです — 新しいコードでは `dayjs` を推奨しますが、Perry は既存のコードベースのために両方をサポートします。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:166
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import moment from \"moment\";\n"
"\n"
"const m = moment().add(7, \"days\");\n"
"console.log(m.format());\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:173
msgid "rate-limiter-flexible"
msgstr "rate-limiter-flexible"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:175
msgid ""
"Native bindings via `perry-ext-ratelimit` (v0.5.552). In-memory limiter is "
"wired; Redis / cluster backing stores are follow-ups."
msgstr "`perry-ext-ratelimit` 経由のネイティブバインディング（v0.5.552）。インメモリリミッターは配線済みです。Redis / クラスタバッキングストアはフォローアップです。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:178
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { RateLimiterMemory } from \"rate-limiter-flexible\";\n"
"\n"
"const limiter = new RateLimiterMemory({ points: 5, duration: 1 });\n"
"try {\n"
"  await limiter.consume(\"ip-1.2.3.4\");\n"
"} catch (rateLimitErr) {\n"
"  console.warn(\"blocked:\", rateLimitErr);\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:189
msgid "worker_threads"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:191
msgid ""
"Partially recognized at HIR-lowering time (`parentPort` / `Worker` shapes) "
"but full dispatch is incomplete. For data-parallel work today, prefer "
"`parallelMap` / `parallelFilter` / `spawn` from `perry/thread` (see "
"[Threading](../threading/overview.md))."
msgstr "HIR 下げ時に部分的に認識されます（`parentPort` / `Worker` の形）が、完全なディスパッチは未完成です。今日のデータ並列処理には、`perry/thread` の `parallelMap` / `parallelFilter` / `spawn` を推奨します（[Threading](../threading/overview.md) を参照）。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:196
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"import { Worker, parentPort, workerData } from \"worker_threads\";\n"
"\n"
"if (parentPort) {\n"
"  // Worker thread\n"
"  const data = workerData;\n"
"  parentPort.postMessage({ result: data.value * 2 });\n"
"} else {\n"
"  // Main thread\n"
"  const worker = new Worker(\"./worker.ts\", {\n"
"    workerData: { value: 21 },\n"
"  });\n"
"  worker.on(\"message\", (msg) => {\n"
"    console.log(msg.result); // 42\n"
"  });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:214
msgid "commander (CLI Parsing)"
msgstr "commander(CLIパース)"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:216
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { Command } from \"commander\"\n"
"\n"
"function commanderExample(): void {\n"
"    const program = new Command()\n"
"    program.name(\"my-cli\").version(\"1.0.0\").description(\"My CLI "
"tool\")\n"
"\n"
"    program\n"
"        .command(\"serve\")\n"
"        .option(\"-p, --port <number>\", \"Port number\")\n"
"        .option(\"--verbose\", \"Verbose output\")\n"
"        .action((options: any) => {\n"
"            console.log(`Starting server on port ${options.port}`)\n"
"        })\n"
"\n"
"    program.parse(process.argv)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:235
msgid "lru-cache"
msgstr "lru-cache"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:237
msgid ""
"The wired constructor takes the npm v7+ options-object shape (`new "
"LRUCache({ max: 100 })`) — the older positional form `new LRUCache(100)` "
"falls through to a `max=100` default."
msgstr "配線されたコンストラクタは npm v7 以降のオプションオブジェクト形式（`new LRUCache({ max: 100 })`）を受け取ります — 古い位置引数形式 `new LRUCache(100)` は `max=100` のデフォルトにフォールスルーします。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:241
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { LRUCache } from \"lru-cache\"\n"
"\n"
"function lruCacheExample(): void {\n"
"    const cache = new LRUCache({ max: 100 }) // max 100 entries\n"
"\n"
"    cache.set(\"key\", \"value\")\n"
"    console.log(cache.get(\"key\"))   // \"value\"\n"
"    console.log(cache.has(\"key\"))   // true\n"
"    cache.delete(\"key\")\n"
"    cache.clear()\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:255
msgid "child_process"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:257
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { spawnBackground, getProcessStatus, killProcess } from "
"\"child_process\"\n"
"\n"
"function childProcessExample(): void {\n"
"    // Spawn a background process\n"
"    const { pid, handleId } = spawnBackground(\"sleep\", [\"10\"], \"/tmp/"
"log.txt\")\n"
"\n"
"    // Check if it's still running\n"
"    const status = getProcessStatus(handleId)\n"
"    console.log(status.alive) // true\n"
"    console.log(`pid=${pid}`)\n"
"\n"
"    // Kill it\n"
"    killProcess(handleId)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/other.md:276
msgid ""
"Two packages live in their own GitHub repos with their own semver — they're "
"imported by `bun add` like any npm package, but Rust-backed and compiled "
"natively via `perry-ffi`:"
msgstr "2 つのパッケージは独自の GitHub リポジトリと独自の semver を持っています — どの npm パッケージとも同じように `bun add` でインポートされますが、Rust で支えられ、`perry-ffi` を介してネイティブにコンパイルされます:"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:280
msgid ""
"**`@perryts/tursodb`** — Turso (libSQL fork) database client. See [PerryTS/"
"tursodb-bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/tursodb-bindings)."
msgstr "**`@perryts/tursodb`** — Turso（libSQL のフォーク）データベースクライアント。[PerryTS/tursodb-bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/tursodb-bindings) を参照してください。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:282
msgid ""
"**`@perryts/iroh`** — Iroh peer-to-peer networking. See [PerryTS/iroh-"
"bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/iroh-bindings)."
msgstr "**`@perryts/iroh`** — Iroh のピアツーピアネットワーキング。[PerryTS/iroh-bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/iroh-bindings) を参照してください。"

#: src/stdlib/other.md:285
